Program: Omnibus
Title: The Gramophone Record
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jgc
Last Broadcast Date: 14 December 1987
Since the patent of the gramophone record in 1887 by Emile Berliner, we have been able to record sound and reproduce it. This programme traces the history and development of the invention of gramophone disc. Picture: Man playing gramophone records, Credit: Getty Images